definition: to start a feud/to become enemies
(of a plant) to produce (fruit or seeds)/Taiwan pr. [jie2]
knot/sturdy/bond/to tie/to bind/to check out (of a hotel)

sentences.english: Pray for the Lord to bring peace to these feuding nations.
